actory\nagreement with observations for 7Li abundance in both young open clusters and\nbinary systems can be achieved if a lower convection efficiency is adopted\nduring the pre-MS phase with respect to the MS one.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Oct 2012 18:25:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 19 Oct 2012 07:27:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
